CBRE and NSL Property Group are pleased to present and available now 96-106 Link Road, Tullamarine.
This high quality fully fitted ‘plug & play office floor is ready to occupy and includes workstations, offices areas, boardroom, comms room and breakout area. COVID friendly environment with both stair access and lift if required. Excellent location for groups seeking quick access to the Airport and Freeway network. 

Key Property Features include:
- Total floor office area: 2000 sqm
- Areas available from 200-2000 sqm
- Ample on-site carparking
- Combination of dedicated and open plan offices
- Modern amenities including shower facilities
- Main road frontage
- Abundant natural light
- Ample on-site car parking
- Access to major arterials
- End of trip facilities

For further details on this property please contact the exclusive leasing agents:
CBRE – Anthony Park – 0403 967 501
NSL Property Group – Guy Naselli - 0413 750 744

CBRE is pleased to exclusively present, For Lease, 38-52 Sky Road, Tullamairne, a major existing distribution centre located within the Melbourne Airport Business Park.  

The Sky Road distribution centre is strategically situated between Melbourne’s Northern and Western industrial markets, providing access to key surrounding infrastructure such as the Western Ring Road, Tullamarine Freeway and Calder Freeway. 

The combination of this infrastructure provides access to all of the key areas of Victoria and Australia via freeway/highway travel for maximum efficiency. 

Key property features include:
+ Total building area: 46,231sqm* (including main office area of 1,024sqm*)
+ Large apron areas that are both open and undercover 
+ Loading from two sides of the warehouse to ensure internal efficiency 
+ 14 recessed loading docks and 11 on-grade roller shutter doors
+ Internal clearance of 11-12.2 metres*
+ Three warehouse office stations for inbound/outbound and warehouse services 
+ Segregated forklift charging area
+ Full drive around capability

For further information regarding this opportunity, contact the exclusive agent, CBRE.

*approx.

***All inspections are undertaken with strict social distancing measures in mind. Live and pre-recorded virtual tours also available. ***


Cargo Park provides an opportunity to occupy premium office and warehouse accommodation in close proximity to the Melbourne Airport with unrivalled frontage and exposure to the Tullamarine Freeway which is one of Melbourne's busiest roads carrying approximately 120,000 vehicles daily. Melbourne Airport - 3.5km*, Port of Melbourne - 22km*, Melbourne CBD - 20km*.

Features include:
+ Office areas from 47.5sqm* to 408sqm* (combined)
+ Warehouse areas from 100sqm* to 1,484sqm*
+ Combined units of office/warehouse available
+ Secure gated estate with 24/7 operation
+ B-double access through central circulation area
+ Ability to park trucks on hardstand
+ Exclusive car bays provided per tenancy
+ Each warehouse includes min 1x container height roller shutter door
+ Walking distance to cafes, restaurants and local shopping centre
+ Fully refurbished and architecturally improved offices
+ NBN available
+ Entrance CCTV
+ Customs bonded tenants present in park
+ Australia's largest domestic industrial listed Landlord

Cargo Park is located at the doorstep of the Melbourne Airport and just 2.8km* from the Melbourne Airport Freight Terminal.

Please contact the marketing agents for further information or to arrange an inspection.

*approx.
